---
By: Jean Anouilh Fortune favors the bold....
Locus:
  Page: 73
  Verse: 1
Tags:
  - Courage
---
To be loved, and to love, need courage; the courage to judge certain values
as of ultimate concern—and to take the jump and stake everything on these
values — Erich Fromm Until the day of his death, no man can be sure of his
courage.
